# Git Workflow

For this project (`contact-center.web`):

- **Do not commit or push** unless the user explicitly asks.
- When asked to commit: stage only relevant changes (skip `obj/`, `.cache`, local config unless requested), write a concise message focused on why, then commit.
- When asked to push: push to `main` (`git push origin main`) unless the user specifies otherwise.
